-- Omega Healthcare to buy Aviv REIT in $3 bln deal 
-- By Natalie Grover in Bangalore
-- Fri Oct 31, 2014 06:33AM EDT
-- None



Oct 31 (Reuters) - Omega Healthcare Investors Inc <OHI.N> said it would buy Aviv REIT Inc <AVIV.N> in a stock deal valued at $3 billion.

Aviv shareholders will receive 0.90 Omega shares for each share held. [ID:nBw73JzNqa] Maryland-based Omega is a real estate investment trust (REIT) investing in and providing financing to the long-term care industry.